            <title><![CDATA[唇周暗沉的姐妹看过来[憧憬]  【34.9】ukiss 女士专用去唇毛漂胡剂  妆容怎么画都画不干净！那就是你的小胡子在作祟啦~这款不仅可以漂胡子，还可以漂手毛、眉毛...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[唇周暗沉的姐妹看过来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[憧憬]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_xingxingyan-c64b6a744b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>【34.9】ukiss 女士专用去唇毛漂胡剂 <br> <br>妆容怎么画都画不干净！那就是你的小胡子在作祟啦~这款不仅可以漂胡子，还可以漂手毛、眉毛都可<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>里面还有漂胡粉、漂胡膏、还有芦荟胶 <br> <br>用法也是想当简单，粉膏混合致粘稠装，漂上个6分钟小胡子几颗变透明☑如果是毛发深的眉毛的话可以漂10分钟左右会浅掉 <br> <br>有一说一，味道有点像染发剂的味道，但是能变美，我忍了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>清洗掉后记得用芦荟胶镇定下哦！<img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afndv0d6j20dv0ip3zt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afneazt9j20e50ijabf.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afner3e6j20dx0hi0ty.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afnf627bj20dv0hp757.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afnfqoq2j20db0h9mxy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afng73nkj20d70f0glx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afngmofnj20dd0gqdg8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afnh1ejej20dr0ipwf8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h0afnhhcxhj20dr0cq3yw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
